name: Carrie Kelly
description: Im a very caring person that likes to be around people that enjoy life and love to have fun. I’m a simple down to earth person who isn’t much into the materialistic things in life. I value the people who come and go in my life and their friendship. I’m a very easy person to get a long with and once you really get to know me you’ll see that I have a lot of love to give and I’m very understanding. I like to travel and see and do different things especially things outdoors.
